{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一回\"一剑穿心\"：深秋古道，名满江湖的剑客燕十三以夺命十三剑轻松击杀前来挑战的\"一剑穿心\"高通。随后关外飞鹰、清风剑、铁剑镇三山、点苍弟子曹冰四人应约而来，燕十三要求四人联手出击，以一敌四仍然秒杀三人，独留曹冰性命，令其练剑三年后再来。暮色中神秘剑客乌鸦现身，此人乌衣乌发，专以收集名剑为乐，已收藏十七柄名剑。乌鸦直言觊觎燕十三的佩剑以及高通等人的遗剑，双方剑拔弩张，一场新的对决一触即发。本章展现了燕十三绝顶的剑术修为和冷漠疲倦的内心世界，同时引出乌鸦这一神秘强敌，为后续剧情埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九月十九，酉时。洛阳城外古道边，古树下。洗净你的咽喉，带着你的剑来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "燕十三？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你的夺命十三剑，真的天下无敌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "未必。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我就是高通，一剑穿心高通。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "是你约我来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "我知道你正在找我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "不错，我是在找你，因为我一定要杀了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "要杀我的人并不止你一个。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为你太有名，只要杀了你，就可以立刻成名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "要在江湖中成名并不容易，只有这法子比较容易。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "现在我已来了，带来了我的剑，洗净了我的咽喉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你的心呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "我的心已死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_tong",
      "speaker_name": "高通",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "那么我就让他再死一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "我只希望你知道，要成名并不是件很好受的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_gao_tong",
      "text": "所以你还不如死了的好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到你们都来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_wai_fei_ying",
      "speaker_name": "关外飞鹰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我本来以为你只约了我一个人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能够一次解决的事，为什么要多费事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_bing",
      "speaker_name": "曹冰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来了四个人，谁先出手？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_jian_zhen_san_shan",
      "speaker_name": "铁剑镇三山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们可以猜拳，胜的就先出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_jian_zhen_san_shan",
      "speaker_name": "铁剑镇三山",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "不必？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们可以一起出手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_wai_fei_ying",
      "speaker_name": "关外飞鹰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你将我们当作了什么人，怎么能以多欺少！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_guan_wai_fei_ying",
      "text": "你不肯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_wai_fei_ying",
      "speaker_name": "关外飞鹰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "当然不肯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我肯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_bing",
      "speaker_name": "曹冰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_cao_bing",
      "text": "我还不想杀你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_bing",
      "speaker_name": "曹冰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_cao_bing",
      "text": "因为我想再给你个机会来杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_cao_bing",
      "text": "你回去，练剑三年，不妨再来杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_cao_bing",
      "text": "点苍的剑法很不错，只要你肯练，一定还有机会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_bing",
      "speaker_name": "曹冰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "三年后你若已死在别人剑下如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_cao_bing",
      "text": "那么你就可以去杀那个杀了我的人。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_bing",
      "speaker_name": "曹冰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你最好多多保重，最好不要死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_cao_bing",
      "text": "我也希望会如此！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我不好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "乌鸦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "想不到我终于还是遇见了你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "遇见我并不是好事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "好剑！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你喜欢剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我只喜欢好剑，你不但有一手好剑法，还有柄好剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你想要？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "喜鹊报喜，乌鸦报的却是忧难和灾祸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你是来报祸的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "我有灾祸？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "我的灾祸就是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "不是你是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "是你的剑！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我已收藏了十七柄剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "十七柄都是名剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "看来你杀的名人也不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "高通和老鹰的剑我要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "收殓他们的尸身，四柄剑都给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
